missionEventData.data1: The Lulsa temporarily escaped from our grasp but the Fogger is already in pursuit. Your squadron is being transferred to our Tie Bombers, and our bomber squadron are prepping a flight of Assault Gunboats. When we exit hyperspace you will bombard the Lulsa and her escorts. After the ship has been crippled the Star Destroyer Hammer will jump in to finish the job as planned. Good luck!
There's the Lulsa. She won't be able to escape this time.
Alpha group we need to take out those Corvettes before the main force can begin its run.
Well done the Corvettes have been destroyed.
We're launching the main attack force now.
Warning a Squadron of X-Wings is launching from the Lulsla.
This is the ISD Hammer. Hope you don't mind if we help finish the job.
Not at all Hammer. Welcome to the fight.
The Rebels are starting to evacuate the Lulsla
Alpha 1 there are still rebel fighters present. Destroy them!
Well done Alpha 1, you can continue to patrol the area or return to the Fogger.
The remaining fighters have been destroyed.
Alpha 1, join the attack against the Lulsla.
The first corvette has been destroyed.

missionEventData.data2: The Empire has been dealt a serious blow! The Emperor's secret weapon, the Death Star, has been destroyed. But justice has been swift. Darth Vader, the Emperor's special envoy, crushed the Rebel base on Hoth and now has the Rebels on the run. High Command have issued a warning to all Imperial outposts, be alert for Rebel forces attempting to flee their base on Hoth. Meanwhile, far out on the Outer Rim, the Imperial Tie Fighter pilot, Maarek Steele, begins his patrol...
